ank you indeed for submitting an actual peer reviewed paper, such a rare treat on a supposed science forum. And it has given us all an opportunity to think about the pros and cons of the methodology. Care to take this on board and expand a little on your now updated thinking?", "recommendation_count": "8", "in_reply_to": "115132427", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "115142448", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1524751872000}, "author": "Craig Thomson", "author_id": "14209233", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "I think the point is it is not low cost energy.The bronze age was a great thing, we moved on from that quite a while ago and are still managing.Your arguments are all straw men, agriculture and medicine have absolutely no need for oil based products. As far as transportation goes you may have noticed the lack of steam trains recently, electric is the way to go.", "recommendation_count": "21", "in_reply_to": "115141814", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "115152604", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1524768653000}, "author": "RattleThatLock", "author_id": "13090116", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Sad but true. And much closer than we think with the biosphere in a state of collapsing and an ice free artic possibly this year ratcheting up the feedback loop acceleration several notches.", "recommendation_count": "4", "in_reply_to": "115145127", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "115155408", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1524777619000}, "author": "Walsunda", "author_id": "12483673", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "The only ones talking about getting rid of capitalism are you and the pu.", "recommendation_count": "4", "in_reply_to": "115135533", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "115146733", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1524757883000}, "author": "EnviroCapitalist", "author_id": "3578530", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Yet another pointless confusing of two themes. Fossil fuels are burnt by pe